Question 1

quartet <- read.csv("Data/Quartet.csv")

Part A

\(\text{X1 Sample Mean} = \frac{10+8+13+9+11+14+6+4+12+7+5}{11}=9\)

\(\text{X1 Sample Median} = 4,5,6,7,8,\textbf{9},10,11,12,13,14 = 9\)

\(\text{X1 Sample Standard Deviation} = \sqrt{\frac{1}{n-1}\sum_{i=1}^{n}{{(x_{i}-\bar{x}}})^2} = \sqrt{\frac{1}{10}[(4-9)^2+(5-9)^2+...(13-9)^2+(14-9)^2]} = \sqrt{11} = 3.32\)

statNames <- c("Sample Mean", "Sample Median", "Sample Standard Deviation")
colNames <- c("x1", "x2", "x3", "x4")

X1 <- mean(quartet$x1)
X1 <- median(quartet$x1)
X1 <- sd(quartet$x1)
